Package org.apache.turbine.annotation

Annotationstyp TurbineService

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({TYPE,FIELD,METHOD}) public @interface TurbineService
Annotation to mark class and fields in modules that require a service to be injected Explicit field annotation of SERVICE_NAME will take precedence of class annotation.
